</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>中國產 Linux 可愛魚 CutefishOS 測試版推出，中國媒體：外貌似足 macOS</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/02/06/cutefishos/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=cutefishos</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Lawton]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Sat, 05 Feb 2022 18:56:35 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[科技趣聞]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1084247</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>中國製造的 Linux 發行版「可愛魚」CutefishOS 0.8 beta 測試版正式推出。這套系統採用簡 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>中國製造的 Linux 發行版「可愛魚」CutefishOS 0.8 beta 測試版正式推出。這套系統採用簡約設計，並引入了流動裝置介面的設計，提升使用體驗。開發者指系統已開放程式碼給全球各地開發者審查以確保沒有 Bug 和後門。</p><p>CutefishOS 由重慶可愛魚科技公司開發，系統基於開源的 Linux 核心所製造，採用簡約設計。程式有通用系統選單列、應用程式視窗的設計，以及內置應用程式的圖示樣式，都有 Apple macOS 的影子。中國傳媒快科技評論，此系統的整體風格與 Apple 的 macOS 有些類似。<a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/1643429296-246683-screenshot-20220129-120629.png"><br /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/menubar.47ce40cd.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1084249" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/menubar.47ce40cd-694x564.png" alt="" width="694" height="564" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/menubar.47ce40cd-694x564.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/menubar.47ce40cd-768x625.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/menubar.47ce40cd.png 878w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/螢幕截圖-2022-01-31-14.36.28.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1084251" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/螢幕截圖-2022-01-31-14.36.28.jpg" alt="" width="522" height="296" /></a></p><p>系統將支援應用程式市場，下載不同應用程式，但目前提供的種類有限。內置應用程式則有檔案管理、截圖功能、系統資源活動監視器、設定工具等等。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/1643429296-246683-screenshot-20220129-120629.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1084248" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/1643429296-246683-screenshot-20220129-120629-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/1643429296-246683-screenshot-20220129-120629-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/1643429296-246683-screenshot-20220129-120629-1280x719.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/1643429296-246683-screenshot-20220129-120629-768x432.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/1643429296-246683-screenshot-20220129-120629.png 1365w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>資料來源：<a href="https://news.mydrivers.com/1/812/812518.htm">快科技</a>、<a href="https://cn.cutefishos.com">CutefishOS</a></p></p><div class="feedflare">
<a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?a=l5mXM0E2Nxs:x2mibiPBl1w:yIl2AUoC8zA"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?d=yIl2AUoC8zA" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?a=l5mXM0E2Nxs:x2mibiPBl1w:qj6IDK7rITs"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?d=qj6IDK7rITs" border="0"></img></a>
</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>懷舊動漫秒變高清  Bilibili 在 Github 發表全新畫質改善技術</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/02/06/bilibili-classic-animate/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=bilibili-classic-animate</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Lawton]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Sat, 05 Feb 2022 18:55:00 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[科技趣聞]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1084286</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>不少用戶在通過網路收看十年前以上的懷舊動畫，畫質大多數只有 360p 甚至更低，在今時今日的標準來說未必能接受 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>不少用戶在通過網路收看十年前以上的懷舊動畫，畫質大多數只有 360p 甚至更低，在今時今日的標準來說未必能接受。中國網路影片平台 Bilibili 近日就在 GitHub 發表全新技術項目，能夠將動漫的解像度提升至 2 倍、3 倍、4 倍，而且支援降噪以及進行錯誤修復。</p><p>系統在 Windows 10、64 位元版本以及 CUDA 10 以上運行，可生成「降噪版」「無降噪版」「保守版」三種圖像類班。「降噪版」適合原影片壓縮過多造成太多訊噪的影片使用；「無降噪版」適合只想提高影片解像度的影片使用，而保守版則在上述模式中出現紋理問題、擔心畫風被改變，不想 AI 處理痕跡過重時使用。</p><p>官方就發出了若干例子，從左至右分別是原版、降噪版、無降噪版以及保守版，可見效果相當顯著。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/title-compare1.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1084287" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/title-compare1-694x109.png" alt="" width="694" height="109" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/title-compare1-694x109.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/title-compare1-1280x201.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/title-compare1-768x121.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/title-compare1-1536x241.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/title-compare1-2048x322.png 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/title-compare1.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/compare3.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1084288" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/compare3-694x173.png" alt="" width="694" height="173" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/compare3-694x173.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/compare3-1280x319.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/compare3-768x191.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/compare3-1536x383.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/compare3-2048x510.png 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/compare3.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/compare2.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1084289" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/compare2-694x130.png" alt="" width="694" height="130" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/compare2-694x130.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/compare2-1280x240.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/compare2-768x144.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/compare2-1536x287.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/compare2-2048x383.png 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/compare2.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/compare4.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1084290" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/compare4-694x98.png" alt="" width="694" height="98" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/compare4-694x98.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/compare4-1280x181.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/compare4-768x108.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/compare4-1536x217.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/compare4-2048x289.png 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/compare4.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>未知此系統是否會在未來引入 Bilibili 平台，現在已發佈在 Github 供下載使用。</p><p><span class="Apple-converted-space"> </span>資料來源：<a href="https://github.com/bilibili/ailab/tree/main/Real-CUGAN">Github</a></p></p><div class="feedflare">
